1.title: About Last Night Part 1
1.plot: In the season 2 premiere, The Caldwell's begin to process Justine's confession surrounding her biological father. Lana's mental state takes a turn for the worse.

imdb.plot outline: In season 1 Maya returns to her hometown after the passing go her father, where she has to face the issues from her past. Season 2, Maya agrees to work with a start up publishing company which keeps in Waterview longer than expected. We are also introduced to brand new characters and double the drama as Maya enters a new relationship. Walker, Lana, Jackson, Kim and Justine try to find direction in their lives after the events of William's repass.
imdb.title: Toll Booth
plot: After the passing of her father, Maya Caldwell leaves the hustle of New York City and returns to her hometown of Waterview, Maryland, a coastal town just outside of Baltimore, Maryland.::Derek Lewis Gray
